<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal;"><strong>Os crit&eacute;rios de avalia&ccedil;&atilde;o dos resumos ser&atilde;o:</strong></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal;">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-add-space: auto; line-height: normal;">Estrutura em conformidade com o conte&uacute;do do resumo;</p>
<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-add-space: auto; line-height: normal;">Adequa&ccedil;&atilde;o do t&iacute;tulo ao conte&uacute;do do resumo;</p>
<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-add-space: auto; line-height: normal;">Respeito &agrave;s normas da l&iacute;ngua;</p>
<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-add-space: auto; line-height: normal;">Objetividade, clareza e concis&atilde;o;</p>
<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-add-space: auto; line-height: normal;">Rela&ccedil;&atilde;o clara com a teoria das representa&ccedil;&otilde;es sociais;</p>
<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-add-space: auto; line-height: normal;">Adequa&ccedil;&atilde;o metodol&oacute;gica;</p>
<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-add-space: auto; line-height: normal;">Aplica&ccedil;&atilde;o/articula&ccedil;&atilde;o dos fundamentos da teoria na an&aacute;lise e discuss&atilde;o dos dados;</p>
<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-add-space: auto; line-height: normal;">Atendimento dos objetivos;</p>
<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpLast" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-add-space: auto; line-height: normal;">Conclus&atilde;o focada nos resultados do estudo.</p>
<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpLast" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-add-space: auto; line-height: normal;">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal;">Os resumos poder&atilde;o ser aprovados, receber <span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp;</span>indica&ccedil;&atilde;o para revis&atilde;o dos autores no prazo inadi&aacute;vel de 7 dias, ou n&atilde;o aprovados. <span style="mso-spacerun: yes;">&nbsp;</span>A revis&atilde;o dos autores ser&aacute; novamente avaliada pela comiss&atilde;o.</p>
<p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" style="text-indent: -18.0pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1;"><span style="mso-bidi-font-family: Calibri; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-latin;"><span style="mso-list: Ignore;">5-<span style="font: 7.0pt 'Times New Roman';"><br /></span></span></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;"><strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"><span style="mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;">Pol&iacute;tica de desist&ecirc;ncia e reembolso do valor de inscri&ccedil;&atilde;o do evento:</span></strong></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; line-height: normal; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;"><span style="mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;">Somente far&atilde;o jus &agrave; devolu&ccedil;&atilde;o do valor de inscri&ccedil;&atilde;o pago, aqueles pedidos formalmente encaminhados, dentro do prazo de <strong>at&eacute; 30 dias </strong>ap&oacute;s a realiza&ccedil;&atilde;o do evento, para a subcomiss&atilde;o de tesouraria do evento. O valor dos reembolsos seguir&aacute; os seguintes crit&eacute;rios:</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;"><strong><span style="mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;">Justificativa do Reembolso</span></strong></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;"><span style="mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;">Mediante a comprova&ccedil;&atilde;o de duplicidade de pagamento do valor de inscri&ccedil;&atilde;o: 100% do valor pago.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;"><span style="mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;">Desist&ecirc;ncia justificada pela n&atilde;o aprova&ccedil;&atilde;o do trabalho cientifico submetido: 80% do valor pago.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;"><span style="mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;">Desist&ecirc;ncia por adoecimento comprovado por atestado m&eacute;dico: 80% do valor pago.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;">&nbsp;</p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;"><strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"><span style="mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;">Observa&ccedil;&atilde;o:</span></strong><span style="mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;"> No caso de o resumo do trabalho aprovado para apresenta&ccedil;&atilde;o estar publicado nos Anais do Evento, o inscrito <strong>n&atilde;o ter&aacute; direito </strong>a devolu&ccedil;&atilde;o do valor de inscri&ccedil;&atilde;o, </span><span style="mso-fareast-font-family: 'Times New Roman'; mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;">quando&nbsp;de&nbsp;sua&nbsp;desist&ecirc;ncia&nbsp;de&nbsp;participa&ccedil;&atilde;o, <strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;">INDEPENDENTE DE SUA &nbsp;JUSTIFICATIVA.</strong></span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: justify; line-height: normal; mso-layout-grid-align: none; text-autospace: none;"><span style="mso-bidi-font-family: Arial;">&nbsp;</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p>
